reviews.text:
The salt and pepper style of cooking pissing shrimp was the best here out of all the places I've eaten.  The shrimp was a little overcooked.  The lobster was well done and the fish soup was good.

You have to pick your seafood in stalls outside the restaurant.  The restaurant only cooks the seafood you picked.
